<s> I don't entirely agree with this.  </s>
<s> I view JavaScript as a means to provide convenience rather than exclusive function.  </s>
<s> However one of the most  </s>
<s> accessible ways I know to do it is have JavaScript generate the elements  </s>
<s> which are providing that functionality.  </s>
<s> For example if you have a button  </s>
<s> which links to javascript.this.print(); then if it is also generated with JavaScript only the people able to use it will have it included in their content.  </s>
<s> In this way I think it is extremely valid to provide redundant or  </s>
<s> more convenient functionality which is also provided by some other server or user agent function.  </s>
